ing content. Finally, we contribute a dataset of\nanonymized clickstreams to the community to foster new studies (anonymized\nclickstreams are available to the public at\nhttp://bigdata.polito.it/clickstream).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 19 Jun 2018 11:25:32 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 4 May 2021 10:37:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-05-05"}
