e the non-interference-based definition is equivalent to\na standard game-based security definition. For the active case we provide a new\nNI definition, which we call input independence.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 19 Jun 2018 12:55:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-12-18"}
