ocks. Our modelling\nprovides a template with which to study the detectability of P-bearing species\nnot only in regions in our own Galaxy but also in extragalactic sources.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 19 Jun 2018 14:34:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-08-08"}
